00:01:08.940 --> 00:01:09.440
- OK.

00:01:09.440 --> 00:01:11.080
What we've got here
is a peace lilly,

00:01:11.080 --> 00:01:14.070
which is native to the tropics,
to a very humid environment.

00:01:14.070 --> 00:01:15.840
It doesn't like our
dry air very much.

00:01:15.840 --> 00:01:17.170
That's part of the problem.

00:01:17.170 --> 00:01:18.480
The other part of the
problem, though, is the fact

00:01:18.480 --> 00:01:20.610
that every time we water,
there's salt in our water

00:01:20.610 --> 00:01:22.200
that accumulates in the soil.

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:23.940
In time, the plant absorbs it.

00:01:23.940 --> 00:01:25.336
