00:01:28.860 --> 00:01:30.660
What we need to do
this plant is repot it

00:01:30.660 --> 00:01:32.720
in a well-drained,
organic potting soil.

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:34.616
It has to stay
moist, but the water

00:01:34.616 --> 00:01:36.240
has to flow through
it easily, as well.

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:37.948
So you might want to
take a potting soil,

00:01:37.948 --> 00:01:39.645
and some sharp sand to it.

00:01:39.645 --> 00:01:41.520
When you repot it,
though, take this one out.

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:43.980
Wash as much of the soil
off the roots as you

00:01:43.980 --> 00:01:45.110
can before you repot it.

00:01:45.110 --> 00:01:46.839
So you remove a
lot of these salts.

00:01:46.839 --> 00:01:48.630
